<div class="container">
  <h5 style="text-align: center;">
    <b>退会</b>
  </h5>

  <div class="row justify-content-center">
    <div class="col-md-10">
      <p>下記の注意事項を確認のうえ、チェックを入れて「退会する」ボタンを押してください</p>

      <div class="withdraw-checked">
        <label>
          <input type="checkbox" name="withdraw_agreement" id="withdraw-agreement">
          退会後、登録内容はできなくなります
        </label>
      </div>

      <div class="withdraw-checked">
        <label>
          <input type="checkbox" name="withdraw_agreement" id="withdraw-agreement">
          既にご注文いただいている商品は、退会後も発送させていただきます
        </label>
      </div>

      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-md-6">
          <%= link_to "退会する", withdrawal_user_path, method: :patch, class: "btn btn-outline-danger btn-block", id: "withdraw-button", disabled: true %>
        </div>
      </div>

      <div class="row justify-content-center">
        <div class="col-md-6">
          <%= link_to "戻る", mypage_path , class: "btn btn-light btn-block" %>
        </div>
      </div>

    </div>
  </div>

</div>
